org.safs.model.tools

Interface EmbeddedHookDriverRunnerAware

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ATest, XTest

    public interface EmbeddedHookDriverRunnerAware
    Classes implementing this interface that get automatically configured by an EmbeddedHookDriverRunner should automatically receive an instance of the EmbeddedHookDriverRunner at runtime.
    See Also:
    AutoConfigureJSAFS, EmbeddedHookDriverRunner.autorun(String[]), Utilities.autoConfigure(String, org.safs.model.annotations.JSAFSConfiguredClassStore)
